### What steps will reproduce the problem?

```
git init test
cd test
git annex init test
git annex upgrade
echo asdf > asdf
git annex add asdf # fails for some reason on DrvFs
git annex add asdf # works when executed second time
git annex sync
git annex --debug adjust --unlock
```


